headline: Healthpeak Properties price target lowered to $22 from $23 at Wells Fargo
summary: Wells Fargo lowered the firm’s price target on Healthpeak Properties (DOC) to $22 from $23 and keeps an Equal Weight rating on the shares. The firm is adjusting price targets across its Healthcare and Net Leasing REIT coverage based on its AFFO yield spread regression analyses and updated NAVs.
